# Keep the Docker build context small + deterministic.
# The Dockerfile COPYs `jido/` and `active_inference/` explicitly.
# Everything else is excluded by default below and re-included with `!`.

**/*

# Required for the build
!active_inference/
!jido/

# Always drop these even under active_inference/ and jido/
**/.git/
**/_build/
**/deps/
**/doc/
**/cover/
**/.elixir_ls/
**/.elixir-tools/
**/erl_crash.dump
**/*.ez
**/mix.lock.backup

# Mnesia on-disk data (never ship dev state into a prod image)
**/priv/mnesia/

# Phoenix generated static caches
**/priv/static/cache_manifest.json

# Local env files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Editor / OS noise
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# Nested Claude / AI scaffolding
**/.claude/
